# CLAUDE.md

Working context for Claude Code sessions in this project.

> **What this file is.** The per-project Claude session contract —
> seeded once by a domain Element's `bin/init` at install time and
> never overwritten. Edit freely; the project owns it forever. The
> Element that governs this project (name, version, pinned SHA) lives
> in `.claude/rasa.lock.json` — this file deliberately does **not**
> hardcode it, so it can't drift out of date.

